Name: (cmol*m2)/kg
Description: Centimole times square metre per kilogram

Name: (cmol*m2*a)/kg
Description: Centimole times square metre times year per kilogram

Name: (mm*m2)/a
Description: Millimetre times square metre per year

Name: cm*m2/d
Description: Centimetre times square metre per day

Name: gal (Imp)
Description: Gallon (Imperial); used in UK, United Arab Emirates for fuels

Name: gal (US fl)
Description: Gallon (US fluid); used in US e.g. for fuel

Name: kWh/m2*d
Description: Kilowatthour per square metre times day

Name: oz av
Description: Ounce (avoirdupois); commonly used, but NOT for gold, platinum etc. (see Ounce (troy))

Name: t*d
Description: Metric tonne times day (1 year = 365 days)
